entries.journal_entry_description: Gather the components listed by Achonnko and he will teach you how to travel Kashyyyk undetected.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Hunt the native creatures to learn the secrets of cover and concealment on Kashyyyk
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Now that you have collected the necessary components, return to Achonnko to learn the secrets of the trail.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: The bone marrow from the Etyyy Mouf makes for an excellent natural camouflage when prepared properly.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: As a fierce predator the Minstyngar is avoided by the other creatures of Kashyyyk. Just the sight of their grey hide or the shake of the horn is enough to provoke other creatures to avoid the Minstyngar at all costs.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: The subtle smell from the Shadevale Venomsting's flesh is quite dulling to the sense of smell. Good for both protection, and it allows the Venomsting to approach prey almost undetected in their natural habitat where smell is often more important than sight.
